{"title":"HTB Keeper","uid":"c25d68859a7c4735b7cbacf72db39f6a","slug":"HTB Keeper","date":"2024-02-06T12:32:40.416Z","updated":"2024-02-06T12:33:44.033Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/HTB Keeper.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/6.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"HTB-Keeper\"><a href=\"#HTB-Keeper\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"HTB Keeper\"></a>HTB Keeper</h1><p>fscan进行扫描</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20240206185853261.png\"></p>\n<p>发现开放了80和22端口，访问下看看</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20240206190639789.png\"></p>\n<p>&#x2F;etc&#x2F;hosts设置下</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20240206190914984.png\"></p>\n<p>发现目标路径是个登录口</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20240206192247347.png\"></p>\n<p>搜索到默认的用户名密码，尝试进行登录</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20240206192357348.png\"></p>\n<p>成功登录，并在Admin-&gt;Users-&gt;Select找到如上界面</p>\n<p>在lnorgaard用户的详情界面找到了备注的pass</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20240206193001832.png\"></p>\n<p>进行ssh登录</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20240206193026525.png\"></p>\n<p>在该目录下起一个python服务，本地wget将zip文件下载下来</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20240206195214189.png\"></p>\n<p>经过搜索知道是个keepass的cve</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/matro7sh/keepass-dump-masterkey\">https://github.com/matro7sh/keepass-dump-masterkey</a></p>\n<p>利用脚本对dmp文件解密出密码</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20240206200759914.png\"></p>\n<p>经过搜索得知</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20240206201932990.png\"></p>\n<p>是一种粥的名称，全称为Rødgrød med fløde</p>\n<p>安装keepassx，apt install即可</p>\n<p>将rødgrød med fløde作为密码打开另一个文件</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20240206202303296.png\"></p>\n<p>在里面寻找到了PuTTY-User-Key-File文件</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20240206202440507.png\"></p>\n<p>利用puttygen生成私钥</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">puttygen 1.txt -O private-openssh -o id_rsa</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>1.txt中的内容就是刚才得到的密钥文件</p>\n<p>生成id_rsa之后，利用id_rsa进行ssh连接</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ssh -i id_rsa root@keeper.htb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://nnnpc-1311441040.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/image-20240206203103603.png\"></p>\n<p><strong>总结：本台靶机的考点在于keepassx的一个CVE和利用puttygen生成私钥进行ssh连接</strong></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"HTB Keeperfscan进行扫描 发现开放了80和22端口，访问下看看 &#x2F;etc&#x2F;hosts设置下 发现目标路径是个登录口 搜索到默认...","permalink":"/post/HTB Keeper","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":614,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"渗透","slug":"渗透","count":5,"path":"api/categories/渗透.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"渗透","slug":"渗透","count":5,"path":"api/tags/渗透.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#HTB-Keeper\"><span class=\"toc-text\">HTB Keeper</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"nnnpc","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/2.jpg","link":"/","description":"安全萌新","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"西湖论剑C0deX战队WP","uid":"6bb955f37944b8dc069388619eaffae8","slug":"西湖论剑C0deX战队WP","date":"2024-02-06T11:03:01.854Z","updated":"2024-02-06T12:34:12.128Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/西湖论剑C0deX战队